node.text:
More than anything else, 2001 A Space Odyssey made me want to be an astronaut.
(cool Pink Floyd Echoes track)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Hadfield on August 26, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: My favorite space food of all. The spicy sauce cuts through the congestion of weightlessness, and the shrimp texture rehydrates well. Good on Earth, too.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Hadfield on August 25, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Earth Venus Mercury 2021 PH27'.

node.text:
Every time we discover a new, big asteroid - like this one, the fastest orbiter we know of - it makes me think of the dinosaurs' lack of a space program.
@carnegiescience
